toggle-decorations (1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Jordi Pujol Palomer ]
  * implement separate options to:
    - option -t : toggle decorations, default
    - option -e : enable decorations
    - option -d : disable decorations
    - option -s : show decorations state
    - Usage:
      toggle-decorations [-t|-e|-d|-s] WINDOW-ID

 -- Jordi Pujol Palomer <jordipujolp@gmail.com>  Wed, 05 Oct 2022 03:38:03 +0200

