    - will not toggle decorations when any second parameter is specified

 -- Jordi Pujol Palomer <jordipujolp@gmail.com>  Tue, 04 Oct 2022 13:58:40 +0200

toggle-decorations (1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Now setnewwinprops uses the C program toggle-decorations.c to set or unset
    window decorations. This C program was done by muktupavels.
    toggle-decorations is not part of the setnewwinprops package because
    it's not licensed and build depends on the hardware architecture.
    However, setnewwinprops may use an alternative method to set or unset
    window decorations tappping keys in the window menu.
    Will build toggle-decorations in a separate package.

 -- Jordi Pujol Palomer <jordipujolp@gmail.com>  Sun, 02 Oct 2022 21:42:43 +0200

